\DOC CBV_CONV

\TYPE {CBV_CONV : comp_rws -> conv}

\SYNOPSIS
Call by value rewriting.

\LIBRARY compute

\DESCRIBE
The conversion {CBV_CONV} expects an simplification set and a term. Its term
argument is rewritten using the equations added in the simplification set.

\EXAMPLE
{
# val rws = from_list (false,[COND_CLAUSES]);
> val rws = RWS<hash_table> : comp_rws;

# CBV_CONV rws (--` (\x.x) ((\x.x) if T then 0 else 10) `--);
> val it = |- (\x. x) ((\x. x) if T then 0 else 10) = 0 : Thm.thm
}

\FAILURE
Should never fail.

\ENDDOC

